dsDescriptionValue.value:
This file contains the geographic items from Summary Tape File 1, as well as total population, provisional population counts by race and Spanish origin, the number of families, and the number of persons in group quarters.

Also included are the number of one-person households, the total number of housing units, the number of occupied housing units, and the number of owner-occupied housing units.

MARF provides summaries and codes for States or State equivalents, counties of county e quivalents, minor civil divisions (MCDs) or census county divisions (CCDs), places or place segments within MCDs/CCDs, remainder of MCD/CCD, census tracts or block numbering areas (BNAs), and block groups (BGs) or, for areas that are not block-numbered, enumeration districts (EDs).
